<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Clown" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Clown,</orth> 1) a rustic, churl: <cit><quote>a swain! a most simple c.!</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.1.142" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 1, 142</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the c. bore it, the fool sent it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 17</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 17</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.4.66" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 4, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 12</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 12</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.616" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 616</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 10, 60</bibl>.<lb />2) buffoon, jester: <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.336" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 336</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 43</bibl> (== fool, 49).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>